	      <rdg source="bib:Sastri1942_01">saindhavānām <lb n="B2"/><unclear>dā</unclear>n<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ā</corr></choice>rthe</rdg>
		<note>N. P. Chakracarti, as editor of Sastri's work, commented in a footnote: <q>Reading or the last two sylables in the first line and of the first two in the second is doubtful.</q> <seg rend="check">Ought one to read <foreign>saindhavāvānartha</foreign> and emend this to <foreign>saindhava-dānārthaṁ</foreign>?</seg></note>
