         <div type="translation">
<p>In the year 4, on day 10 of the waxing fortinight of Caitra during the reign of Śrī Mahendrapāladeva <supplied reason="subaudible">the image</supplied> was set up by Kumārabhaṭṭa as a gift to the Saindhava <supplied reason="explanation">monks</supplied>.</p>
